      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_51_01-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "あら、まだ白紙なの？　先週聞いた時は「やりたい\nことがあり過ぎて困る～」って言ってたわよね？",
      "startTime": 25.9999993007,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
